org.osgi.service.clusterinfo

Interface FrameworkNodeStatus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FrameworkManager, NodeStatus

    public interface FrameworkNodeStatus
extends NodeStatus, FrameworkManager
    The FrameworkNodeStatus service represents a node in the cluster that is also an OSGi framework.
